{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The Mixologist</i> brings the art of cocktail crafting to life in an immersive virtual reality experience. Whether you\u2019re a seasoned bartender or new to the craft, the game offers over 100 real-life cocktail recipes to master in single player campaign or multiplayer co-op modes. Mix, shake, and garnish drinks with precision, honing your skills through intuitive and rewarding gameplay, or attend the bars as a patron and allow your friends to make your favorite cocktails for you in an inviting social environment. \ud83c\udf79 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/GIFF_14_New.gif?t=1731691157\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore five distinct bars, each with its own unique atmosphere and challenges. From the cozy neighborhood pub to the bustling rooftop lounge, each venue offers a fresh experience, requiring you to adapt and refine your bartending techniques. As you progress, unlock new recipes and venues, eventually earning your place as a legendary mixologist. \ud83c\udf78 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The gameplay blends authenticity with arcade-style fun, making it easy to pick up, but challenging to master. Points are earned based on speed and skill, adding a competitive edge as you strive to perfect each order.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/header01.png?t=1731691157\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/GIFF_01_new.gif?t=1731691157\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/header02.png?t=1731691157\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/GIFF_13_New.gif?t=1731691157\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/header03.png?t=1731691157\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/GIFF_11_New.gif?t=1731691157\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/header04.png?t=1731691157\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160660/extras/GIFF_17.gif?t=1731691157\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Why Mixologist?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Mixologist combines fast-paced challenges with the fun of mastering your bartending skills. Whether playing solo or with friends in co-op mode, you\u2019ll find a blend of creativity, strategy, and fun that keeps the good times rolling! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Join the Community:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Connect with other players and share your bartending journey. Compete on global leaderboards, exchange tips and tricks, and become part of the vibrant Mixologist community.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"A star is born","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3160660/0c53cefe4570edacd151afbe3afafa742dafc49d.jpg"},{"name":"Shaketastic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3160660/30f5158b9d175fe1d6eb345ee517c290ac68463f.jpg"},{"name":"Fruitness","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3160660/a5eb8751885306bbcbe51d088cde446a2d7398ce.jpg"},{"name":"Just water please","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3160660/9e1c09c8c671639ae0ea946fc40754e9207c088b.jpg"},{"name":"Buddy","path":"https://cdn.a